{"tid":1538414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新 嘅 訴 求：我 哋 將 會 補 上","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:00:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T08:49:40.000Z","uid":107699,"like":36,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"adec468023ac1c662d03dfc8e99395290f90a732","tid":1538414,"uid":107699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:00:46.000Z","msg":"我想講撒回送中條例成句係<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「 撒 回 送 中 條 例，並 承 諾 任 期 內 唔 會 再 推 」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咪撚比佢做一半呃到！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n就算搞掂一樣 重有千千萬萬樣呀！<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好唔記得先至得架！<br />\n<br />\n排緊隊嘅有：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">1. 撒回監控燈柱<br />\n2. 撒回明日大嶼<br />\n3. 拎返150隻蝗審批權<br />\n4. 重有大把... </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記得！五大訴求係唔可以間斷！直至贏返香港為止！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"5331c4400c1277a9a78f7285b5edc53ed17857a5","tid":1538414,"uid":107699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:01:03.000Z","msg":"自推10次！"},{"pid":"5bcda8a110ddd6327a6d8eb233e6ea19fd46615e","tid":1538414,"uid":107699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4584437d8265ff1f3380322ac74f42a2ff9b9d9e","tid":1538414,"uid":107699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:01:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e85bbfd30efe274dee0456a32936371322ae35b5","tid":1538414,"uid":107699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:01:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.