By":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:03:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"521f0b8374c218fa92f426699afe009212afb196","tid":1538414,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:03:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2fe1a20ee3483ceb0459ffca1cf7ed400c320284","tid":1538414,"uid":91558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:03:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"74241fa9ca150c43d402add32d11bd3926a26ad1","tid":1538414,"uid":290815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:03:25.000Z","msg":"大家要到幾時先察覺，靠政府去實現五大訴求已經變成一個好恐怖既局？<br />\n<br />\n[時光倒流Re-post] 香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538204</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先大家可以選擇服用咗以上文章先<br />\n<br />\n然後我可以反問一句，有冇人諗過五大訴求真係實現既情況會係點？<br />\n<br />\n係，的確可能證實到瘋狂既民意係可以改變到政府所作出既決定，但下次兩地一檢呢？再下次智慧燈柱、全面普教中呢？反送中2.0、3.0發生，真係好？點解要跟住個垃圾政權條尾走？<br />\n<br />\n香港人，唔好再「<span style=\"color: red;\">要求</span>」政府畀到五個願望你哋，請大家一齊親手達成依五個，甚至一百個願望都得，可唔可以？<br />\n<br />\n睇唔明我講咩既話請讀上面篇文章一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a14501644d615ff9c30ed751962ee4b38108e9a","tid":1538414,"uid":258068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:03:51.000Z","msg":"150隻蝗可唔可以插隊補上"},{"pid":"e685e9877adb5af0a183c4c53b21232af07074a8","tid":1538414,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:03:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1048ea20de0d5a197822965db93145accab54ac4","tid":1538414,"uid":107699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5129af54cf4d7db3ace7d6a4a555101fa894728","tid":1538414,"uid":40826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:02:09.000Z","msg":"其實呢句係唔夠<br />\n因為下個任期又可以再推過..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:04:39.000Z","msg":"本身想講28年內唔好再推<br />\n<br />\n但... 唔識講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以最緊要真。雙普選！</span></span>"},{"pid":"dec377fcb642ae403a10565aee53146b1a3e69eb","tid":1538414,"uid":187820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:06:25.000Z","msg":"三個月 都係唔識分撒同撤<br />\nBtw 五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"4e70bc242d8bbc63d4786c14e6ba78e86e9b8b30","tid":1538414,"uid":107699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:07:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">總之所有惡法都要推晒出來 一齊過搞掂！<br />\n<br />\n唔好比港共中共走呀！</span></span>"},{"pid":"f21446b9a34234c765099b53553f573bb3dbf50d","tid":1538414,"uid":107699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dec377fcb642ae403a10565aee53146b1a3e69eb","tid":1538414,"uid":187820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:06:25.000Z","msg":"三個月 都係唔識分撒同撤<br />\nBtw 五大訴求 缺一不可"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:08:25.000Z","msg":"Sor Ching<br />\n有時打開果粒字 錯開有條路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"908df38bd08b85b04753a9b38def2a8f8dd876db","tid":1538414,"uid":299254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:09:38.000Z","msg":"解散警隊<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"4fd47095fa05d7e50e4c03b5d6438b67d1f8bf40","tid":1538414,"uid":295304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:11:15.000Z","msg":"有冇見過兇殺案由政府新聞處公佈？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535010\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535010</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n睇埋回覆先留言，因為分析我放咗喺回覆<br />\n<br />\n成個熱門勁多都係講林鄭撤回嘅風，<br />\n但而家佢撤唔撤回都好，831太子站有冇死人、有冇極嚴重傷勢受害人，呢d都係要查啊！<br />\n唔好俾佢轉移焦點啊！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好認真，點解一路發生咁多件事，都冇話撤回，突然今日會講起？到底呢幾日發生咗咩事逼到佢要做野？係咪真係其實死咗人？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要求黨鐵交出831太子站完整CCTV記錄啊！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"cf1832fe9ae297bc9700d3650482b51791dda87e","tid":1538414,"uid":187820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f21446b9a34234c76